Various infosec tools

Copyright 2011 Olivier Bilodeau <olivier@bottomlesspit.org>

Latest version available at: https://github.com/obilodeau/infosec-tools

The tools
---------

* Crypt::rotn

  Tired of rewritting the same simple code over and over again to break simple 
  rot-based substitution ciphers so I decided to create a perl module.

Bug reports / contributions
---------------------------
Are more than welcome! Ideally use github but bug reports and patches by email
will do fine.

